diffrence between stringbuffer and stringbuilder-->>
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
string buffer-->>
							1.	it is thread safe,multiple thread cant access at the same time.
							2.  it is mutable,we can modifing string without creating an object
string builder-->>
									1. it is not thread safe,faster than string buffer.
									2. it is also mutable 










